text: Metković is a city in the Dubrovnik-Neretva County of Croatia. Metković may also refer to: * RK Metković (Rukometni Klub Metković) is a handball club from Metković, Croatia. * Metković (Bogatić), a village in Serbia **Mačvanski Metković **Pocerski Metković ==See also== *Matković, a Serbo-Croatian surname
